options.text: Why are you called Longbow Ben?
Have you got any quests I could do?

69565e36-498d-4d8f-a261-15ea2e4ee95d.title: <player>
69565e36-498d-4d8f-a261-15ea2e4ee95d.text: Why are you called Longbow Ben?

2a59ef32-edc2-42f8-9b27-19b1dfc11cbb.title: Longbow Ben
2a59ef32-edc2-42f8-9b27-19b1dfc11cbb.text:
I was to be marooned, ye see. A scurvy troublemaker
had taken my ship, and he put me ashore on a little
island.

2cf1d2b4-3acd-4afb-95dc-99c8e7f0747b.title: Longbow Ben
2cf1d2b4-3acd-4afb-95dc-99c8e7f0747b.text:
Arrr, ye see, he made one mistake! Before he sailed
away, he gave me a bow and one arrow so that I
wouldn't have to die slowly.

739f2f20-6b71-47fa-8b90-c6567144a479.title: Longbow Ben
739f2f20-6b71-47fa-8b90-c6567144a479.text: So I shot him and took my ship back.

42d0065d-6a50-4cf0-8b29-fb093ecbb329.title: <player>
42d0065d-6a50-4cf0-8b29-fb093ecbb329.text: Have you got any quests I could do?

c157c5be-1082-4058-a610-8eb3677ed2b9.title: Longbow Ben
c157c5be-1082-4058-a610-8eb3677ed2b9.text: Nay, I've nothing for ye to do.

956ce249-3949-4706-8c78-dcad562918f4.title: Longbow Ben
956ce249-3949-4706-8c78-dcad562918f4.text: Nay, always ye say it wrong! Tis 'we are', not 'we be'.

128a09b7-e17c-4b24-b0b3-f1a9ca9b4e91.title: Jack Seagull
128a09b7-e17c-4b24-b0b3-f1a9ca9b4e91.text: I be a pirate, not a scurvy schoolmaster!

ab3a8890-67eb-4cf2-b6b4-28f980c6df95.title: Longbow Ben
ab3a8890-67eb-4cf2-b6b4-28f980c6df95.text: Ye be a fool, and a disgrace to piracy.

7c9d501a-f7c9-4ef5-be2a-399b98326e6a.title: <player>
7c9d501a-f7c9-4ef5-be2a-399b98326e6a.text: I think I'll leave you two to sort it out.
